      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/247908.Bee_Wilson">About Bee Wilson</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/247908.Bee_Wilson"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_111x148-9394ebedbb3c6c218f64be9549657029.png);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/247908.Bee_Wilson">Bee Wilson
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
155
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer16874973310736708578">Beatrice Dorothy &quot;Bee&quot; Wilson (born 7 March 1974, Oxford) is a British food writer and historian. Wilson is married to the political scientist David Runciman and lives in Cambridge. The daughter of <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/5842160.A_N__Wilson' title='A.N. Wilson' rel='nofollow noopener'>A.N. Wilson</a> and the Shakespearean scholar <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/139094.Katherine_Duncan_Jones' title='Katherine Duncan-Jones' rel='nofollow noopener'>Katherine Duncan-Jones</a>, her sister is Emily Wilson, a Classicist at the University of Pennsylvania.</span>
  <span id="freeText16874973310736708578" style="display:none">Beatrice Dorothy "Bee" Wilson (born 7 March 1974, Oxford) is a British food writer and historian. Wilson is married to the political scientist David Runciman and lives in Cambridge. The daughter of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/5842160.A_N__Wilson" title="A.N. Wilson" rel="nofollow noopener">A.N. Wilson</a> and the Shakespearean scholar <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/139094.Katherine_Duncan_Jones" title="Katherine Duncan-Jones" rel="nofollow noopener">Katherine Duncan-Jones</a>, her sister is Emily Wilson, a Classicist at the University of Pennsylvania.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16874973310736708578" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

